

KASALANAN

   root word: [66]sala
   kasalanan
   fault, error, mistake, blame, sin

   Kasalanan ko ba ito?
   Is this my fault?

   Kasalanan mo ito.
   This is your fault.

   Kasalanan ba ang magmahal?
   Is it a sin to love?

   Gobyerno ang may kasalanan.
   The blame lies with the government.

   Kung kasalanan ang mahalin ka…
   If loving you is a sin…
   = If loving you is wrong…
